d NFT drops as a unique\nsource of market congestion -- holiday effects -- beyond trend and season\neffects. Finally, we envision three future research directions of TFM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 May 2023 05:17:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-05"}
